A vintage-style illustration of a fox sitting at a cluttered wooden workbench, carefully organizing and sorting dozens of colorful puzzle pieces into neat rows. The fox wears old-fashioned round spectacles and uses a magnifying glass to examine each piece. The workshop has warm amber lighting from an antique desk lamp, shelves lined with small glass jars containing various mechanical gears and springs, and aged blueprint papers pinned to cork boards in the background. The color palette features warm oranges, deep browns, and muted teals, with a slightly faded, nostalgic quality reminiscent of 1950s technical illustrations.
